de.tlabs.mobileCloud.benchmarkBundle2
Class revcomp

java.lang.Object
  de.tlabs.mobileCloud.benchmarkBundle2.revcomp

public class revcomp
extends java.lang.Object

We use the FASTA file generated by the fasta benchmark as input for this benchmark. Note: the file may include both lowercase and uppercase codes. Each program should read line-by-line a redirected FASTA format file from stdin for each sequence: write the id, description, and the reverse-complement sequence in FASTA format to stdout We use these code complements: 

 code meaning complement
 A      A                T
 C      C                G
 G      G                C 
 T/U    T                A
 M      A or C           K
 R      A or G           Y
 W      A or T           W
 S      C or G           S
 Y      C or T           R
 K      G or T           M
 V      A or C or G      B
 H      A or C or T      D
 D      A or G or T      H
 B      C or G or T      V
 N      G or A or T or C N
Adapted for PowerDroid framework by Andrius Aucinas

Author:
Andrius
